 (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/K%E1%BB%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng/author-03ZNaWfxP9_K2e7vJXYXyw">Kỳ Đồng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/Ti%E1%BB%83u-k%C3%ADnh/poem-smtOoSQiq19W-DakFuCKBA">Tiểu kính - 小徑</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/author-qoi_3MEdeZkoj0TClsekFA">Ngô Dung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Ti%E1%BB%83u-nhung-3/poem-bpr_uOvYC71QFSE2Z5fj2Q">Tiểu nhung 3 - 小戎 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C6%B0-th%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%A9-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-h%E1%BB%99-Vi-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-linh-th%E1%BA%A5n-quy-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-%C4%91%C3%B4-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-SEjMfGgEFsz4fgzn0vpr0Q">Tống Lư thập tứ đệ thị ngự hộ Vi thượng thư linh thấn quy thượng đô nhị thập vận - 送盧十四弟侍禦護韋尚書靈櫬歸上都二十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
